Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Britons are too happy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0409q8c
Last Broadcast Date: New Year's Day 1978
Survey finds Britons are happy - despite lack of national economic growth. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.